        <source>getJMTReleaseExtractTime() : TimeStamp;
/*

Purpose:			Get the date and time that this version of the source was extracted from
					the JMT development environment as a full cut.
					This method is automatically updated by the release cut process.

Parameters:			None

Return Value:		TimeStamp that the extract was run

Date		Who		Reason
17 Sep 2015	cnwkpd1	Monthly releases - need an extract timestamp embedded in the release

